---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-white/5 bg-black px-6 py-16 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <span class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter text-white">
          Ouro<span class="text-[#D4AF37]">&</span>Navalha
        </span>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50">
          Excelência em barbearia clássica e moderna. Onde a tradição encontra o luxo para o homem contemporâneo.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:col-span-2">
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#D4AF37]">Localização</h4>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-white/60">
            <li>Av. Paulista, 1000</li>
            <li>Jardins, São Paulo - SP</li>
            <li>(11) 99999-9999</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#D4AF37]">Horários</h4>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm text-white/60">
            <li>Seg - Sex: 09h às 20h</li>
            <li>Sáb: 09h às 18h</li>
            <li>Dom: Fechado</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 border-t border-white/5 pt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 sm:flex-row">
      <p class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/30">
        © {currentYear} Ouro & Navalha. Todos os direitos reservados.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="#" class="text-white/30 hover:text-[#D4AF37] transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg></a>
        <a href="#" class="text-white/30 hover:text-[#D4AF37] transition-colors"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
